{"tid":587650,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[傑出父母系列］看圖作故事","createTime":"2018-03-10T14:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T11:08:00.000Z","uid":175677,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39b01f06673e432ace8605250e6942acd76330a3","tid":587650,"uid":175677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/222937_20c4bb3d908a4ecbbe857b9bbdd97f3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F222937_20c4bb3d908a4ecbbe857b9bbdd97f3c.jpg&h=d95480d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/10/223455_65846ce1b89a184c8cba60539a8c345a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F10%2F223455_65846ce1b89a184c8cba60539a8c345a.jpg&h=61f6535b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先行過樓下，我見到咁既情景：<br />\n垃圾桶則邊有紙碟，檸檬茶盒同一大堆四散既垃圾<br />\n仲有張大海報添<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道咁多樣野有無關聯，所以我唯有請大家一齊<br />\n祝Lok小朋友生日快樂全家幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母過2條街有垃圾站唔去就咁掉係街？<br />\n正一含家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891d627307fde727c02362d80caaea741dea59cc","tid":587650,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"依家啲小朋友生日會真係會搞到好大陣仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申細個連M記生日會都冇開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd88ba521383edeca151d375c432a38691c59edb","tid":587650,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c31769a599eae0f4991f152c506af3ede9d2718d","tid":587650,"uid":1